'''Claire Hiatt''' interviewed [[Jackson Avery]] for a job at UCLA.

==History==
Claire had Jackson come to UCLA to interview there. He impressed her with his skill, but he was put off when she asked about him asking [[Harper Avery|his grandfather]] to come speak there and he walked out of the interview.

==Career==
She is a doctor who works at UCLA. She interviewed Jackson for a job.
